                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Comic Book Realms -->
                <div class="content-card rounded-lg">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-tertiary-primary">Fictional Cartographies: The Heavens & Hells of Comics</h3>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">Modern fiction, particularly comics, has visualized the "beyond" in ways that reflect contemporary scientific and philosophical ideas. These realms are often depicted not as static places but as fundamental, cosmic structures or higher-dimensional planes.</p>
                    </div>
                     <div class="image-gallery grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-b-lg">
